[div class=p 
	"The map is structured in a main map that called the Castle and 5 submaps that called the World. To open the doors that are led to next Worlds, we have to find the Keys in the Castle and Worlds. The 1st Key is obtained at once, but the other Keys are defended by the bosses in each World. Therefore, it is necessary to make the rounds of the Worlds. 
	$LF
